text: Mela Lee McLean (born July 31, 1976) is an American voice actress based in Los Angeles who voices characters on a number of animated series, movies, television shows and video games. She is best known for voicing Jade in Mortal Kombat 11, Superstar in SparkleGlobe Witches, Tikki in Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir and Socks Heeler in Bluey. ==Other websites== * * Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Los Angeles Category:American voice actors
